use of the\npopulation inversion factor. The presented theoretical framework is applied to\na numerical study of a two-section distributed Bragg reflector laser.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 2 May 2021 19:14:58 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 5 Jun 2021 19:09:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-07-01"}
