iability is intrinsic to the primary star that is still recovering from the\nGreat Eruption with a decreasing mass-loss rate and a polar wind that is\nevolving at a slower pace than at the equator.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 3 May 2021 01:07:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 11 May 2021 12:59:40 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 13 May 2021 01:07:28 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Sat, 5 Jun 2021 13:39:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-08"}
